item.title: CVE-2017-6154|2024-08-05T15:18:49.947Z -- f5%20networks%2C%20inc. -- big-ip%20asm
item.description: On F5 BIG-IP systems running 13.0.0, 12.1.0 - 12.1.3.1, or 11.6.1 - 11.6.2, the BIG-IP ASM bd daemon may core dump memory under some circumstances when processing undisclosed types of data on systems with 48 or more CPU cores.
